Head.
Head 1.8, 1.5 × as wide as long anteriorly (except mandibles) and dorsally respectively; antenna with 19 flagellomeres (

); tyloids present on flagellomeres 8–13 (

); frons (

) reticulate-punctate posteriorly; vertex reticulate- punctate behind stemmaticum and near eyes, becoming spaced punctate posteriorly (

); OOD 2.6 × POD (

); OOD 3.0 × OD; occipital carina narrow, non-lamelliform, smooth (

); supra-antennal elevation medium-sized, about 0.4 × as long as scape (

